CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 16, 1951, pg. 9 reads: "...Pitt Queen - At the annual...ceremonies at the University of Pittsburgh...ay, Elaine Hall, shown in ....an attendant to the "Senior Queen" at the coronation ceremony in the Commons Room. Miss Hall was graduated from the college on Wednesday. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Virginia Elaine Hall, attendant to "Senoir Queen," wearing light colored short sleeved dress and crown, walking on Bigelow Boulevard with Pittsburgh Athletic Association building in background
